      "writtenOn": "2019-01-10T02:14:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "renaming jobs is actually non-trivial: some may rely on at most 1 build running at the same time.\nSo trade off is:\n 1) easy migration now \u0026\u0026 difficult later for more projects with more configs \nVS\n 2) difficult now \u0026\u0026 easier later\n\nbut \"later\" is conditional on actually switching scheduler to buckets, which is currently postponed. So, i think I agree with your decision.",
      "parentUuid": "fa8dd8ed_cde19824",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 356,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 358,
        "endChar": 75
      },
      "revId": "441646694b112ddd636112dbe1a36a577d0ad2f0",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
